ibelief 1.1
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Add the function LCRule for creating bba from probabilities using Least-Commit Princple
  
* Change the form of the input and output mass matrix for function discounting. Now for both the input and output mass matrix, each columb is a bba. If there is only one bba to discount, the input and output bbas are both vectors. 
   
* Fix the bug that qtow function could not work for dogmatic belief functions. 

* Fix the bug that wtoq function could not produce an output 
     
